            },
            "answer_text": "Yes, you can do that.  Feifei Wang's answer to Can I buy a book from Barnes & Noble and then return it after reading it? is great.  The only thing that I will add is that if you do it repeatedly, they will notice and talk to you about it.  A friend of mine used to work at Barnes & Noble, and she told me that they had one customer in particular who had a pattern of buying books and then returning them a few days later.  One of the managers called  her on the phone and offered to \"personally help her choose books that she would like to keep in her permanent collection\" or something along those lines.   ",
